  <trk>
    <name>Edelweiss path (Höhbalmen) (No. 30)</name>
    <desc>Seeing an edelweiss in the mountain meadow once in a lifetime is the dream of every mountain walker. Here the dream becomes true. The edelweiss shine, sometimes even at eye level along this path! The hike leads to one of the most beautiful viewpoints in the Zermatt area.</desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
